query:
SELECT pi.url, pi.fileKey, p.name 
FROM product_images pi 
JOIN products p ON pi.productId = p.id 
WHERE p.slug IN ('wutai-lamp-offering', 'wutai-incense-offering') 
AND pi.isPrimary = TRUE 
LIMIT 2;
